title: DVS "iPandemonium!" FULL TOUR VIDEO
description:
Originally appeared
In conjunction with Thrasher Magazine, the DVS squad invades Costa Rica, Panama, and Peru, slaying demos while still handling lots of business in the streets. Torey caps things off with that massive nollie flip from Thrasher's March cover. Boom!
